---
{/* Grüns-style impactful stats section */}
<section class="bg-stone-100 py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center tracking-tight mb-10">
      You're probably dehydrated right now.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-medium">75%</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-foreground/60">of Americans are chronically dehydrated</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-medium">70%</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-foreground/60">of brain function depends on proper hydration</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-medium">2%</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-foreground/60">drop in hydration causes a 20% drop in performance</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-medium">0</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-foreground/60">grams of added sugar in every Purest jar</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
